      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The leaflet promotes the ‘first feature film produced in Romania’. The leading actor, Lilly Flohr, is described as the greatest German actress of the Reinhardt school. The text adds that director Jean Mihail is to welcome the audience in the Romanian language.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">‘Lya’ (a woman’s first name) was produced by ‘Indro Film’ and released in 1927.</ab>
